videos.headline: Xavier Moon makes hustle play and then buries one from NBA range

videos.description: Morehead State guard Xavier Moon dives into the crowd to save a loose ball and hustles back into the play in time to bail out the Eagles with a deep 3-pointer to beat the shot clock.
